# SHACL spec §2.1.3.4 — sh:targetSubjectsOf data graph.
# Source: https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl/#targetSubjectsOf
# The shape targets subjects of ex:knows. The shape requires sh:nodeKind sh:IRI.
# ex:Alice is an IRI subject → conforms.
# ex:Bob uses ex:livesIn (not ex:knows) → not targeted.
PREFIX ex: <http://example.com/ns#>

ex:Alice ex:knows ex:Bob .
ex:Bob ex:livesIn ex:NewYork .
